OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder over
OL,4,CLurgan police station car bomb
OL,6,FA 48-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith a number of offences, including
OL,8,Fattempted murder, in relation to an
OL,9,Fattempted car bomb attack on Lurgan
OL,10,Fpolice station in March.
OL,12,FThe dissident republican group the New
OL,13,FIRA claimed responsibility.
OL,15,FThe incident saw a food delivery
OL,16,Fdriver hijacked in Kilwilkie and
OL,17,Fforced to drive a "crude but viable"
OL,18,Fdevice to the station.
OL,20,FThe device failed to explode.
OL,26,@yD@SOUyD@dO]
