OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778198576
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder over
OL,4,CLurgan police station car bomb
OL,6,FThree people were arrested on
OL,7,FWednesday by police investigating the
OL,8,Fincident.
OL,10,FOn Thursday evening, the PSNI said
OL,11,Fthey had charged a man with attempted
OL,12,Fmurder, attempting to cause an
OL,13,Fexplosion, hijacking and possession of
OL,14,Fexplosives with intent to endanger
OL,15,Flife or damage property.
OL,17,FHe is due to appear at Craigavon
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Friday May 8.
