OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder over
OL,4,CLurgan police station car bomb
OL,6,FEarlier this week, a 39-year-old woman
OL,7,Fwas arrested in relation to the same
OL,8,Fincident and charged with obstructing
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FShe was released unconditionally in
OL,12,Frespect of perverting the course of
OL,13,Fjustice and assisting an offender.
